        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34381735/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34381735/" class="">第268页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2301686/" class=" " title="上古的埙">上古的埙</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="34381735">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">有人写信给赫尔岑：“我感谢你，正如农夫感谢雨水使他缺乏养料的土地恢复生机一样。”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-02-23 21:24</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                有人写信给赫尔岑：“我感谢你，正如农夫感谢雨水使他缺乏养料的土地恢复生机一样。”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

